            ],
            "effect": "The nilith reaches into the mind of the grabbed creature and implants disjointed images of the victim's worst fears and nightmares. The grabbed creature takes 6d6 mental damage with a DC 31 basic Will save. On a critical failure, the target is also affected as though by *never mind*, and it must attempt a second Will save against that effect.",
